# Getting started with Calendly

To use any of the above modules, you need to connect your Calendly account to Integromat. If you do not have a Calendly account yet, you can create one at [Calendly.com](https://www.calendly.com/).

## Connecting the Calendly service to Integromat

To connect your Calendly account to Integromat, follow the general instructions for [Connecting to services](https://support.integromat.com/hc/en-us/articles/360001990194.html#create-a-connection). When creating a connection, you will be requested to enter your API Key. A quick quide to getting an API key can be found [here](https://developer.calendly.com/v1/docs/getting-your-authentication-token). Once you have copied your API key to Integromat, click on **Continue** and finish your scenario.

![Connection](https://integromat.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360009136774/file.png)
